data.title: Jeff Anderson Filmography, List of Jeff Anderson Movies and TV Shows
data.meta_description: Films starring Jeff Anderson. Also features Jeff Anderson TV shows. Latest movies featuring Jeff Anderson. Jeff Anderson DVDs. The list includes TV series, TV movies, short films and movie appearances. The filmography list includes the title, the title's year of release, and the character played by Jeff Anderson, where applicable.
data.text:
Clerks III 2022

Randal, executive producer, the director would like to thank: For being so great in Clerks II that I spent ten years trying to get Clerks III made. - as Jeff

Dante, Elias, and Jay and Silent Bob are enlisted by Randal after a heart attack to make a movie about the convenience store that started it all. more »

Director: Kevin Smith

Writer: Kevin Smith

Clerks II 2006

Randal, the director would like to thank: For not only coming back, but for knocking it out of the park and keeping me honest. - as Jeff, performer: "The Invisible Guests"

A calamity at Dante and Randal's shops sends them looking for new horizons - but they ultimately settle at the fast food empire Mooby's. more »

Director: Kevin Smith

Writer: Kevin Smith
